---
import Button from '../components/Button.astro';
import { Img } from 'astro-imagetools/components';
---
<div class="container">
    <div class="content">
        <h3 class="title">
            <div class="title-icon">
                <img src="/images/conversion-title-icon.svg" alt="" width="150" height="80">
            </div>
            まずはお気軽に説明会にお越しください
        </h3>
        <div class="body-text">
            <p>これはダミーのテキストです。ここにはよくある質問の回答が入ります。これはダミーのテキストです。これはダミーのテキストです。ここにはよくある質問の回答が入ります。<br>これはダミーのテキストです。これはダミーのテキストです。ここにはよくある質問の回答が入ります。これはダミーのテキストです。これはダミーのテキストです。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="button">
            <Button href="" label="見学してみる" size="large" width="full" iconSrc="/images/icon-visit.svg"/>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="bg">
        <div class="bg-image rellax" data-rellax-speed="-2" data-rellax-percentage="0.55">
            <Img src="/images/conversion-bg.png" placeholder="none" format="webp" alt="" />
        </div>
        <p class="bg-note">STUDIOつくば　非公式キャラクター「ツクロウくん」</p>
    </div>
</div>
<style>
    .container {
        position: relative;
        z-index: 0;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        justify-content: center;
        min-height: min(92.5vh, 760px);
        padding: 80px 0 80px 80px;
        width: calc(var(--content-width) / 2 + 50%);
        margin: 0 0 0 auto;
        color: var(--color-white-primary);
        border-radius: 80px 0 0 80px;
        overflow: hidden;
    }
    .content {
        width: 55%;
        padding: 0 0 24px;
    }
    .title {
        font-size: 40px;
        margin: 0 0 28px;
        text-shadow: var(--text-shadow-primary);
    }
    .title-icon {
        width: 150px;
        margin: 0 0 16px;
    }
    .body-text {
        line-height: 2;
        margin: 0 0 48px;
        text-shadow: var(--text-shadow-primary);
    }
    .button {
        width: 100%;
        max-width: 480px;
        position: relative;
    }
    .button::before {
        content: "";
        position: absolute;
        inset: -16px;
        background: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
        border-radius: 36px;
        animation: conversion-button-bg 1s 0s normal both infinite ease-out;
    }
    @keyframes conversion-button-bg {
        0% {
            opacity: 1;
            inset: 0;
            border-radius: 24px;
        }
        100% {
            opacity: 0;
            inset: -32px;
            border-radius: 36px;
        }
    }
    .bg {
        position: absolute;
        inset: -2px;
        z-index: -1;
        background: radial-gradient(circle at center top, var(--color-orange-secondary),var(--color-orange-tertiary));
        filter: url(#chromaticAberration) url(#chromaticAberration);
    }
    .bg::before {
        content: "";
        position: absolute;
        inset: 0;
        z-index: -1;
        opacity: 0.25;
        mix-blend-mode: screen;
        background: url("/images/bg-pattern-secondary.svg") center/20px repeat;
        -webkit-mask: radial-gradient(circle at center,transparent,#fff);
        mask: radial-gradient(circle at center,transparent,#fff);
    }
    .bg-image {
        position: absolute;
        right: 0;
        bottom: 40px;
        width: 52.5%;
    }
    .bg-note {
        position: absolute;
        right: 0;
        bottom: 24px;
        text-align: right;
        padding: 0 24px 0 0;
    }
</style>